t the parliamentary dissolution and announcement of election by the government was in accordance with the constitution. \u201cThe government move cannot be stated unconstitutional as the constitution itself has enshrined the provision that the parliament could sustain for five years on condition it is not dissolved\u201d, the minister argued.\n\nHe also urged the cadres not to cast any doubt regarding the conduction of elections in the country.","title":"Internal feud behind dismal performance of government-Minister Dhakal - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/02/153685/","video":[]}
